Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,The date not the day of the week‎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Um..‎
