Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Do you remember your mother's name?</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>How about your father?</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>This is an experimental procedure.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.72,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Electrodes will send impulses</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>to the target areas in your brain.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.68,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>New neural pathways should develop,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.82,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but the results can be a little less predictable‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:23.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,especially given your history of substance abuse‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,a common trigger for Alzheimer's‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.93,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Is this Roy Freeman?</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:54.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Hello?</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.16,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah <i>Um, my name is Emily Dietz.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I work with the Clean Hands Project.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.16,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Clean Hands Project?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:04.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Yes!</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>We are a legal action nonprofit</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>and we advocate for inmates</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>who have been disenfranchised by the system.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:12.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Would you have a few minutes to speak?</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.57,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What's this about?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>It's... regarding an old case of yours.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Emily Dietz‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Freeman? - Ms. Dietz‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.16,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. Hi‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:49.91,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Emily - Emily‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I really appreciate you meeting with me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No problem‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.95,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You said it was about uh, an old case, huh?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:58.57,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Isaac Samuel‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Isaac Samuel?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:07.23,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Um... I... I'm sorry I-I don't, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. Of course‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:09.71,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've seen more cases‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:10.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,than you care to remember‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.41,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Something like that‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.37,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He was convicted in the Joseph Wieder murder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,at Waterford College ten years ago‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:20.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and is scheduled to be executed‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.33,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,end of next month‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We've tried to get a stay from the governor‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.38,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but it's not looking good‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't recognize him‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.38,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What's he got to do with me?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Samuel requested to speak with the detectives‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:36.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,who had interrogated him the night of his confession‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I interrogated him?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:40.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And I have yet to locate your former partner‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.74,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What does he want to talk about?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm afraid he didn't say‎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.44,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,That's something that you will have to ask him yourself‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.68,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Isaac Samuel?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:21.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:29.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Roy Freeman I used to be a detective‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:31.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been told you wanted to see me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Yeah? - Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.35,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, here I am‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,How are you doing?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:47.62,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, you know I'm blessed, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:50.41,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Ten years three hots and a cot‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,member of the death row book club‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:55.11,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Prison got my body but Allah got my spirit‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:57.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Like you give a fuck how I'm doing‎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:10:59.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I see‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:05.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So, this lady uh... Emily Dietz‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.29,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,from the Clean Hands Project‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:08.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,she told me you wanted to talk to me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:10.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that what you wanted to say?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No, you're here 'cause I want to know how it feels‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:15.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,to know an innocent man is gonna be put to death‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Right‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And, uh... you are the innocent man?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.83,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.40,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.05,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd done some bad shit made some bad decisions‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.58,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but killing Joe Wieder ain't one of them‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Isaac..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:33.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,you confessed‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You were brought in for questioning‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:37.28,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and you confessed‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:40.24,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So now you're telling me all this time later‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:41.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,suddenly you remember things different?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Ain't nothing sudden about it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:46.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been in here ten years Ten fucking years‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:49.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing to do but replay that shit in my head‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.68,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- How it really went down - Right‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.38,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So you can tell me how it really went down‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, I know you ain't no cop no more‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.56,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,the way they shit-canned you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:01.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,over that drunk-driving accident‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.74,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but maybe you want to clear your conscience‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:07.44,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,At least hear me out.. this time‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:11.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm listening‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Night of the murder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.80,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I was so strung out I ain't remember shit‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.76,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>You guys hammered me all night.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>By the time I saw those photos, I was so fucked up</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.06,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I thought I must have done it.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You broke in you beat him to death‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We found your fingerprints all over the house‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:33.12,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Just admit it, son. Admit it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:37.16,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,This was you. This was you You did this! This is you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.82,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,This is all fucking you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:42.56,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Admit it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:43.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.70,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Why did you go to his house?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.27,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,The year before Wieder got killed‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.05,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I got rung up for theft‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Formula for my little man‎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:13:00.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And Wieder testified as an expert witness for the DA‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.49,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I told the judge I was so high that night‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.02,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking straight‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but Wieder said I knew exactly what I was doing‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.41,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So they tried me as an adult‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You know what it's like to be 18 years old‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:12.29,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and some skinhead's bitch?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's just go back over this‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wieder testifies against you and gets you prison time‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You go to his house, it's late at night. You're angry‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:23.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't like this--I ain't no killer‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.35,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I just wanted my son back‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.74,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and I thought maybe Wieder could help‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.96,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Yeah, I went to his house.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I waited for his caretaker to leave</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.70,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>and I went round the back.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I even made it all the way inside.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.41,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello, Shadow‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:57.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>But then someone else came in.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:14:00.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh! Back so soon?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.04,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>And then shit just went bad.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:08.30,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.74,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I panicked and I left before I could see who it was.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,[Wieder] No‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:20.70,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. So you never touched him‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:24.05,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh, but you don't... I'm telling you the truth‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, Isaac‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You think I'm lying‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:45.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, ask Richard Finn He'd tell you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to remind me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:52.95,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Um... who-who is Richard Finn?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He came to see me a few months back‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He's writing some book about the murder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- A book? - Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:04.49,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, uh Isaac, I just don't see‎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,that I'm gonna be in a position to get involved‎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.71,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You already involved, Roy This is on you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You were there when I signed that fucking confession‎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:15.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Make it right‎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:17.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I paid for what I did when I was 18‎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Make this shit right or I'm dead‎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.84,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>The medication can aid synaptic regeneration,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.06,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>but you must keep your mind active--</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:56.89,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>books, puzzles, anything to stimulate your brain.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:11.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It was you It was you! Admit it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.12,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You did this! This is you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:15.38,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, ask Richard Finn‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:16.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:22.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Roy?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:24.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.19,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What the fuck are you doing here?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I was just in the neighborhood‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.64,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Come in‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Come in come in, come in‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Come in, come in‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:50.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, I can't remember the last time I saw your face‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:53.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,There you go, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:57.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You know when it was?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.84,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Ahh, it must have been ten years ago‎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,when those fucking sons of bitches took your badge‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:04.93,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I suppose so‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:13.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen, I hope you're not still carrying around all that shit‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:16.81,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, we all drank on the job back then‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,That accident‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,that could have been any one of us‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:23.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Cheers‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:24.90,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Cheers‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:32.26,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What's up? You on the wagon or something?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh... well, yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:37.92,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,My-my doctor says it'll mess with my medication, so..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You're sick, Roy?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:43.10,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No. I'm doing, uh like a clinical trial‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:45.10,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I've got Alzheimer's‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:49.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,so they put these little pulses into my fucking head‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It's supposed to stimulate memory‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,If you hadn't have said my name at the front door‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.81,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have known it was you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So you..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:03.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,you have no memory of you and me on the job?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- No - Fuck‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:07.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I-I read old case files‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:10.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and it's all fresh information for me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's not just my time on the job‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,My whole fucking life is a black hole. I..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuck, man‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:22.70,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Remember Cat?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.62,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,My wife‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, she, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.19,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,she passed last year‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:36.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Cancer‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:38.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry - Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.02,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Fucking cancer‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:43.63,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Department health fund‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,wouldn't pay her hospital bills‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.38,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I had to sort it out‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.38,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, you didn't come here for that shit‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:54.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What brings you by, Roy?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:59.82,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. Uh... you remember a guy called Isaac Samuel?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He got convicted for murder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.26,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,that thing that happened at Waterford College‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.70,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,with a professor?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Ahh. You've been talking to the lady‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:09.27,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,from the advocacy group‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:12.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't call her back‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:15.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I took the call‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:19.71,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and, uh, she said that Isaac wanted to talk to me, so..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You spoke to Isaac Samuel?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:26.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. I went down to the state prison‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:28.81,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and we talked and, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,he tells me he didn't do it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:35.86,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on, Roy. That's what they all say on death row‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:37.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, I know‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:42.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But I gotta say, Jimmy he was... convincing‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:46.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He mentioned another guy that came to see him. Uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.57,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Finn‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.36,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Richard Finn‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.49,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Does that name ring any kind of bell with you?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:02.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It was so long ago I-I-I don't remember..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:04.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I read the file‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.28,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and when we dusted that house‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:11.68,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Finn's prints are all over the place inside‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:12.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,All through the house‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:17.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,They were there. Who cares?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:19.38,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Richard Finn said he wasn't at the house‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,the night of the murder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.56,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,That's in his statement, okay?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:24.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But we never followed it up‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:26.74,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We never corroborated his whereabouts‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and I just kinda found that a bit strange‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:30.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that not strange?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:34.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What's your point?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:35.96,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:37.57,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that you and me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.18,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,we'd maybe go and talk to him‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:41.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,see what he has to say for himself‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.62,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Why? - I don't know‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:45.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It's just a feeling‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:47.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,That's all I got to go on these days‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:51.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides, my doctor says I gotta keep my mind active‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:53.02,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,so what the fuck, huh?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:56.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:59.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll look into it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:01.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I still got a few friends on the job‎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:05.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:09.56,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be in touch, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:11.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>♪ You ♪</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:13.71,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>♪ What do you see? ♪</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:21.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:37.26,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah <i>I found your boy.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:39.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I found Richard Finn.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:44.44,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,The landlady found him when she let the gas man in‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:46.22,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,How did he die?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:51.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Overdose. Fentanyl‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:57.41,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Only one needle hole‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.15,0:23:59.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:01.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He's not much of a junkie‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:02.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,There's no track marks‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:04.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So he's a newbie Didn't know what he was doing‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.04,0:24:19.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- You alright there, Roy? - He was there‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.43,0:24:21.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,At the crime scene‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.78,0:24:23.91,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Yeah. You said that - No‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.05,0:24:25.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No, not just his prints‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.61,0:24:29.09,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He was there the next morning when we were there‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.22,0:24:30.62,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Is this what you're remembering‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.75,0:24:32.10,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,seeing him at the crime scene?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.32,0:24:36.84,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,This guy's prints are at the house. All over it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.97,0:24:39.19,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He turns up to the crime scene the next morning‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.93,0:24:41.28,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We talk to him‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.41,0:24:43.63,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,His alibi for the time of the murder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.76,0:24:45.41,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,is that he was home alone‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.54,0:24:46.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And we don't follow it up‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.72,0:24:47.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We don't talk to his friends‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.11,0:24:49.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,we don't talk to his neighbors‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.59,0:24:52.68,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Isaac Samuel's prints were all over the house‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.81,0:24:56.16,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He had motive and he confessed‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.29,0:24:58.12,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense‎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.25,0:25:01.39,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter now The dead don't talk‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.13,0:25:03.00,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.00,0:25:05.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But they do leave shit behind‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.87,0:25:10.05,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,From ashes to ashes from dust to the dust‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.18,0:25:11.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,so it must be‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.35,0:25:14.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, God the spirit of all our joys‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.01,0:25:16.92,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,the cause of our delights‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.05,0:25:20.36,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,the glory of our darkest nights‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.93,0:25:24.41,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh, Mrs. Finn?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.24,0:25:26.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,My name's Roy Freeman‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.67,0:25:27.72,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.20,0:25:29.89,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I understand this is a very bad time‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.02,0:25:31.90,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but can I just ask a couple of questions‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.03,0:25:33.68,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,about your husband?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.81,0:25:36.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh... I'm her husband, Eddie‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.51,0:25:38.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so sorry, Eddie‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.12,0:25:42.30,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi. Uh... is the other Mrs. Finn around here somewhere?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.43,0:25:43.91,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh, no‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.04,0:25:46.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She and Richard weren't exactly on the best of terms‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.30,0:25:48.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, is there something I can help you with?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.26,0:25:50.22,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He was my brother‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.13,0:25:52.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm looking into a case‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.66,0:25:55.09,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,that your brother was particularly interested in‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.61,0:25:57.92,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Recently he went to visit a death row inmate‎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.05,0:26:00.10,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and he mentioned he was actually writing a book‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.23,0:26:01.49,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,on the subject‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.62,0:26:03.27,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I wondered if you knew anything about this‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.41,0:26:05.02,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get a ride home with Aunt Jude‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.15,0:26:06.06,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Yeah - Okay?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.19,0:26:07.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay - Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.89,0:26:14.29,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm, uh... just over here‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.51,0:26:20.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Here‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.60,0:26:22.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I found it in his apartment‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.16,0:26:24.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He called it <i>The Book of Mirrors.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.86,0:26:26.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,The title doesn't make any sense to me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.86,0:26:28.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Book of Mirrors...</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.21,0:26:32.30,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Isaac Samuel that, uh, death row inmate‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.43,0:26:34.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,he said this is about the Wieder murder?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.74,0:26:36.44,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, well if Richard were here‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.57,0:26:39.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,he'd probably call it a crime memoir or some shit‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.14,0:26:41.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You read it?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.14,0:26:42.36,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Much as I could stomach‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.49,0:26:44.40,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a bunch of self-aggrandizing garbage‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.53,0:26:45.93,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,you ask me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.06,0:26:47.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,About some girl he was obsessed with in college‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.45,0:26:50.37,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So, uh, you guys weren't close?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:52.24,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, I don't mean to speak ill of the dead‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.37,0:26:53.72,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but Richard wasn't exactly someone‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.85,0:26:55.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,that you wanted to get close to‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.15,0:26:58.81,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,How long had he been using?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.94,0:26:59.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Drugs?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.11,0:27:01.81,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No. No‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.94,0:27:03.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I never knew him to be into drugs‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.68,0:27:06.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It just didn't seem his thing Then again, with Richard‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.82,0:27:09.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,nothing was ever really how it seemed‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.95,0:27:11.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, he'd always been a little bit off‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.91,0:27:13.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,even when we were kids‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.69,0:27:16.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but this last year last couple of years, even‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.57,0:27:18.39,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,something just didn't seem right‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.52,0:27:19.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What was different?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.79,0:27:21.35,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know. He was..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.83,0:27:24.62,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,agitated, paranoid‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.84,0:27:27.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Just like he comes across in that book‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.79,0:27:29.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, listen, if I were you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.01,0:27:31.58,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I wouldn't waste too much time on it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.76,0:27:35.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. I can keep this?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.45,0:27:36.93,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Be my guest‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.09,0:28:05.92,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"Memory is a fickle thing.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.05,0:28:08.49,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>What we can recall what we can't.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.27,0:28:11.49,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Rare moments that forever imprint,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.49,0:28:14.06,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>banalities that don't.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.67,0:28:18.32,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Sufferings so painful,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.45,0:28:21.20,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>they're buried deep in our mind's recesses,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.33,0:28:23.46,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>forgotten till time digs it back up.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.03,0:28:29.81,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Whatever the memory, though-- good, bad, unremarkable--</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.94,0:28:31.90,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>it never comes back all at once.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:34.56,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>They're always doled out in fragments</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.69,0:28:38.04,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>like pieces of a puzzle you have to wait to complete."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.87,0:28:44.22,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"When you'll get another puzzle piece...</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.35,0:28:45.83,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>that's anyone's guess.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.13,0:28:51.49,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Months, years could be a decade."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.62,0:28:53.27,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Richard Finn‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.40,0:28:56.01,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"Like it was with the murder of Joseph Wieder.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.67,0:29:02.50,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Ten years of never understanding it."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.11,0:29:09.90,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"Or as I now know misunderstanding it."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.03,0:29:12.64,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,No‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.86,0:29:17.77,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"And all because of her.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.60,0:29:21.26,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Laura Baines.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.17,0:29:25.22,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>She was one of those rare unicorns</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.35,0:29:27.65,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>who knew everything about everything."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.78,0:29:29.44,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Nobody made better use of chromatic counterpoint‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.57,0:29:30.61,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,than Rachmaninoff‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.74,0:29:31.96,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"Double bachelor's in</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.09,0:29:33.75,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>art history and neuroscience."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.88,0:29:36.97,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,...between lower cortisol levels and their predisposition..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.10,0:29:38.53,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"A master's in math."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.66,0:29:41.10,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,The beauty of what Odlyzko showed‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.23,0:29:42.45,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,is that the distribution..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.58,0:29:43.67,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"Spoke five languages."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.89,0:29:53.29,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"She knew exactly who she was.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.51,0:29:57.42,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>If only I did back then."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.65,0:30:08.17,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,How's the punch?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.13,0:30:12.44,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,The way you've been skulking around‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.57,0:30:14.48,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,waiting for your moment to come and talk to me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.61,0:30:16.75,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I figured you'd at least come up with something better than‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.88,0:30:18.27,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,"How's the punch?"‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.88,0:30:20.31,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I wasn't skulking‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.44,0:30:22.58,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Not just skulking Leering too‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.71,0:30:24.14,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh! Skulking <i>and</i> leering‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.27,0:30:26.32,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,You're making me sound like I'm a serial killer‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.45,0:30:28.41,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I can say I knew you when‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.89,0:30:33.81,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm, uh, Richard - I know‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.07,0:30:36.20,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,It's on your chest‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.94,0:30:38.33,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. Right‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.98,0:30:40.60,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,And yet, uh, here you are‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.73,0:30:42.81,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,nameless and shrouded in mystery. Seems unfair‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.95,0:30:44.43,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,"Oh, what's in a name, really?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.56,0:30:46.64,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,That which we call a rose by any other name."‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.78,0:30:47.69,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, great‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.82,0:30:49.30,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Another bardolater‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.82,0:30:52.22,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,So, uh, what's your thesis about?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.35,0:30:54.04,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Um... No! Don't tell me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.17,0:30:55.65,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- Let me guess. Okay - Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.78,0:30:58.44,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh... it's probably something controversial‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.57,0:30:59.70,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- Probably - Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.83,0:31:02.83,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, "Cross Gender Interference‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.97,0:31:04.27,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,in <i>A Midsummer Night's Dream."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.40,0:31:05.36,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Boom‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.49,0:31:06.53,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Close‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.66,0:31:08.10,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,"Memory Reconsolidation‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.23,0:31:10.41,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Through Accelerated Resolution Therapy."‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.54,0:31:12.80,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. One of the Bard's lesser known works‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.76,0:31:17.89,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Um..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.02,0:31:20.42,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Psychology department I'm Laura‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.72,0:31:25.20,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,What, you just like to crash other departments' mixers?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.34,0:31:27.03,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, no I came with a friend‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.16,0:31:29.38,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, a colleague, really Professor Wieder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.12,0:31:33.21,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm helping him with some research‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.34,0:31:34.65,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,and he's administering my thesis‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.78,0:31:35.69,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Right‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.82,0:31:37.04,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,On memory reconstruction‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.17,0:31:39.04,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,through the accelerated reconciliation?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.18,0:31:40.96,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,"Memory Reconsolidation Through..."‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.09,0:31:42.48,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.61,0:31:44.49,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,No. Sorry. I'm just being hard on you now‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.62,0:31:46.01,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,It is a bit of a mouthful‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.75,0:31:51.06,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,How many wishes do you get?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.45,0:31:54.02,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.15,0:31:56.11,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,It, uh... It belonged to my grandmother‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.24,0:31:57.76,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I read somewhere‎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.89,0:32:00.28,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,that, uh, when a woman plays with her jewelry‎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.41,0:32:01.85,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,it means she's flirting with you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.98,0:32:04.16,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh! Really? Hmm‎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.77,0:32:07.07,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, you shouldn't believe everything you read‎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.42,0:32:09.55,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.18,0:32:33.19,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Choke me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.97,0:32:34.97,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,What?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.10,0:32:36.45,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Do it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.19,0:32:39.37,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Harder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.89,0:32:42.37,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.13,0:33:07.96,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"From that moment on,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.09,0:33:09.79,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>it was like we were inseparable."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.44,0:33:14.44,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"For the next few months,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.58,0:33:16.19,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>we did everything together.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.06,0:33:22.15,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>She made me feel like the best version of myself."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.63,0:33:29.33,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,So... what do you think?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.72,0:33:32.98,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,What do I think?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.12,0:33:36.21,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I think you're fucking brilliant, Richard‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.34,0:33:38.56,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, other people need to read your work‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.69,0:33:41.38,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,You should send it to.. to <i>Harper's, The Atlantic,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.52,0:33:43.78,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,all the big fiction rags‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.91,0:33:45.61,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"It was like I was experiencing the world</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.74,0:33:47.87,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>for the first time through her eyes."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.35,0:33:50.35,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- You're so talented - Thanks‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.79,0:33:53.61,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Just, uh, one second. Sorry‎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.01,0:34:00.27,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.40,0:34:02.27,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"But not everything was looking rosy."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.06,0:34:04.32,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh-huh‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.45,0:34:05.67,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"A few months after we met,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.80,0:34:07.76,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>my father died of a heart attack.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.89,0:34:10.41,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>My mother couldn't afford my room and board.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.41,0:34:13.46,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Laura wanted to help</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.59,0:34:17.12,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>and that's how I first met Professor Joseph Wieder."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.08,0:34:23.21,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Laura. Welcome‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.34,0:34:24.65,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry we're late‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.78,0:34:26.82,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- Not a problem - Hi‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.95,0:34:27.95,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.35,0:34:32.52,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Had to finish a call with our friend in DC, anyway‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.65,0:34:34.66,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- Ah! Mm-hm - Mm-mm‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.35,0:34:36.66,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,You must be Richard‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.79,0:34:38.09,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Laura's told me a lot about you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.96,0:34:40.14,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,All lies, I'm sure‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.27,0:34:41.97,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Exaggerations and half-truths‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.10,0:34:43.53,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Those I can live with‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.66,0:34:45.10,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Do we feel like martinis?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.23,0:34:46.75,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- Sure - Yes‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.93,0:34:54.24,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,So, Richard, Laura tells me you want to be a novelist‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.37,0:34:56.33,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Literary memoir, actually‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.46,0:34:57.77,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- Mmm - Oh?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.68,0:34:59.68,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not familiar‎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.81,0:35:01.12,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, you see‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.25,0:35:02.81,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,a traditional memoir is someone's life story‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.94,0:35:05.29,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,The genre's not concerned with questions of truth‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.42,0:35:08.04,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,imagination, memory, style‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.17,0:35:10.65,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Literary memoir has a fictional element, then?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.78,0:35:12.65,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, I wouldn't call it fictional, really‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.78,0:35:14.35,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- No - Oh. Sorry‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.52,0:35:17.00,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,No, you see, uh, the author's‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.13,0:35:18.39,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,telling the truth of the story‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.52,0:35:19.83,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,as he believes it to be true‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.96,0:35:21.75,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,They. As <i>they</i> believe it to be true‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.88,0:35:24.05,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Self-perception and personal experience‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.18,0:35:25.49,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,have a part in it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.62,0:35:26.71,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.54,0:35:32.50,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,More wine?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.63,0:35:33.98,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- Please - Yes‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.15,0:35:40.63,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,You know something?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.76,0:35:42.03,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Ten years from now..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.16,0:35:43.33,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,we'll look back to this dinner‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.46,0:35:44.81,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,and all we'll remember is‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.94,0:35:46.55,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,the Chateau Leoville Barton‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.68,0:35:48.95,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I doubt that‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.08,0:35:51.56,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,The mind replaces memories all the time‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.69,0:35:53.21,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,It's innate to its wiring‎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.00,0:35:56.08,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Especially if you drink too much‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.40,0:36:04.40,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Do the thing‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.53,0:36:06.44,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Hmm?[Laura] Come on‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.57,0:36:08.49,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not a party trick‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.62,0:36:10.84,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait. What is she talking about?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.97,0:36:12.80,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,It helps explain what we're working on‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.63,0:36:18.37,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, then. Pick a memory. Hmm?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.50,0:36:20.11,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,From your childhood. Anything‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.24,0:36:22.63,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Objects, moments, people‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.76,0:36:25.03,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Anything you can easily recall?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.72,0:36:27.16,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.38,0:36:30.55,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay Uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.25,0:36:34.78,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I remember we had this green shag rug‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.91,0:36:36.56,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,and, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.69,0:36:38.95,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,...four goldfish‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.08,0:36:40.48,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,named after the guys in KISS‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.91,0:36:43.31,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a good memory‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.44,0:36:46.70,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,How about something that you wish you could forget?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.92,0:36:49.09,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Um..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.22,0:36:50.70,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Did your parents ever hit you?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.62,0:36:55.80,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,No‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.93,0:36:57.19,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Did you ever get lost‎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.32,0:37:00.58,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,in a shopping mall or a big supermarket?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.98,0:37:05.37,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean... come to think of it there was this one time‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.50,0:37:08.20,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,we went to a toy store and, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.46,0:37:12.12,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I... I couldn't find my mom‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.25,0:37:13.73,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Were you scared?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.55,0:37:17.03,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, I haven't thought about it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.17,0:37:18.64,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,since it happened, but..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.30,0:37:20.21,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.34,0:37:21.78,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I looked for her everywhere‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.91,0:37:23.74,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,And you eventually found her?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.48,0:37:28.05,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh... outside smoking‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.96,0:37:33.14,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh. It's... crazy‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.01,0:37:36.23,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten all that‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.80,0:37:42.76,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,At the, uh... the heart of our research, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.67,0:37:45.50,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Joe's research‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.63,0:37:49.11,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,is the thesis that most people experience trauma‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.24,0:37:51.29,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,but the mind blocks those memories‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.42,0:37:53.64,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,from ever actually presenting‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.77,0:37:55.59,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,The trauma you experienced that day‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.73,0:37:57.60,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,was your mother abandoning you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.73,0:37:59.99,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,You were a child. Vulnerable‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.12,0:38:03.69,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,And that fact that your mother might actually harm you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.82,0:38:05.87,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,is too traumatic to process‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.00,0:38:08.91,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,So you suppressed it from memory‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.04,0:38:11.61,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,But the effects of that trauma‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.74,0:38:13.61,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,still linger in your subconscious‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.74,0:38:16.62,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,and become part of the fabric of who you are‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.31,0:38:20.40,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Wow. Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.53,0:38:21.62,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,That's..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.75,0:38:23.23,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Therapy with dinner‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.36,0:38:24.80,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Cheers‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.68,0:38:33.76,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Richard‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.42,0:38:35.72,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Would you come with me?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.85,0:38:38.42,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I've got something I'd like to show you. Hmm?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.42,0:38:40.86,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.87,0:38:58.74,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay That's a lot of books‎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.88,0:39:02.31,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I can offer you $500 a week to organize it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.84,0:39:04.93,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,To classify them electronically‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.06,0:39:07.41,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,when you can, until you're done‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.54,0:39:10.23,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,which, if I had to guess won't be anytime soon‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.89,0:39:15.02,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I... I mean, I don't really know what to say. Uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.15,0:39:17.59,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Laura told me about what happened to your father‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.72,0:39:19.46,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,and the situation that you're in‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.77,0:39:24.25,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,So you might want to just say you'll do it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.08,0:39:27.51,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.78,0:39:33.04,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"Working for Wieder was a dream.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.65,0:39:37.26,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>New worlds opened up.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.70,0:39:41.48,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>A curated collection of the world's greatest thinkers.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.92,0:39:49.84,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>For every two I'd catalog...</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.71,0:39:53.67,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I'd find myself reading another.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.33,0:40:00.72,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Eventually, though, all the time I spent at Wieder's</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.85,0:40:03.20,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>exposed me to something I wasn't expecting."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.99,0:40:09.34,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- More books? - Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.47,0:40:11.17,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,The professor wants me to donate them‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.30,0:40:12.99,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,but there's some good shit in here‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.95,0:40:19.04,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Say, uh, what's with the bats?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.00,0:40:20.96,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,His dad's‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.09,0:40:22.57,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Collected them, I guess‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.13,0:40:25.57,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Signed too‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.70,0:40:28.36,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Willie McCovey. Al Kaline‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.49,0:40:29.84,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Ted Williams‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.31,0:40:31.97,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,You wanna finish this? I gotta work‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.97,0:40:33.97,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sure‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.10,0:40:35.62,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.12,0:40:52.38,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"A laugh."</i> Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.51,0:40:53.95,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"A hand grazing an arm."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.73,0:40:57.43,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"One thing's clear."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.48,0:41:04.96,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Hey, it's me.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.09,0:41:06.96,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I'm sorry, but I have to bag on dinner tonight.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.09,0:41:08.44,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I'm stuck at the office helping Joe,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.57,0:41:10.49,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>but I'll, uh... I'll see you when I get home.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.88,0:41:14.45,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"Laura Baines was more than</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.58,0:41:16.75,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>just Joseph Wieder's research fellow."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.03,0:41:36.73,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to be working‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.43,0:41:41.26,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't you have a research paper due tomorrow?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.39,0:41:43.13,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.26,0:41:45.91,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I have so many patient notes to transcribe‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.96,0:41:52.01,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.62,0:41:57.23,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, God Do you like that?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.36,0:41:58.92,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,You know I like that‎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.06,0:42:01.01,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,[Laura] You know I do‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.76,0:42:08.06,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"Despite our time together,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.20,0:42:10.02,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I didn't know Laura Baines at all."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.25,0:42:24.99,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"And when I found that manuscript...</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.91,0:42:28.91,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I realized I wasn't the only one."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.04,0:42:30.70,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.83,0:42:33.92,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, hey. I didn't know you were home‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.00,0:42:37.83,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- What have you got there? - I don't know‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.96,0:42:39.36,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I found it in, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.49,0:42:41.32,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,It was lodged in the back there behind some books‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.45,0:42:43.36,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. Huh‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.49,0:42:46.15,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Laura. So eager‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.89,0:42:47.97,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh‎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.06,0:42:51.98,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on Before lunch gets cold‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.99,0:43:05.08,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you like to cook, Richard?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.56,0:43:07.86,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't really know how‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.99,0:43:10.30,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, you should learn‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.43,0:43:13.13,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe you're good at it maybe you're not, hmm?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.39,0:43:15.61,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Experiment‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.74,0:43:17.31,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Mm-hm‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.44,0:43:20.05,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Laura likes a man who can cook‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.44,0:43:24.62,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,How are things going between you two?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.53,0:43:27.71,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,We're just friends‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.84,0:43:29.41,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, come on‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.06,0:43:32.28,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I got the impression you were more than that‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.41,0:43:34.19,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that what she told you?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.32,0:43:36.28,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't need Laura to tell me something to know it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.41,0:43:37.89,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I can sense things‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.02,0:43:39.81,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I've known her for some time now‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.85,0:43:42.99,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Right. I mean I-I would never presume..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.12,0:43:45.94,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,But, Richard, she brought you into my life to help‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.08,0:43:48.12,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,not to complicate things‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.25,0:43:50.65,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,And that's what I'm here for to help‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.78,0:43:52.21,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, good‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.78,0:43:54.39,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,To that end, then‎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.35,0:43:58.65,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I think-- and these are just my thoughts--‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.00,0:44:03.61,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I think it would be better if you stopped seeing each other‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.62,0:44:06.01,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, what?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.62,0:44:09.27,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Nobody likes it when things‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.40,0:44:11.67,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,become overly complicated‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.84,0:44:18.11,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going out of town to meet some people about my book‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.80,0:44:21.07,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I imagine when I get back‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.20,0:44:23.98,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,you will have sorted out some new arrangement‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.25,0:44:27.60,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Bon appétit‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.86,0:44:32.38,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"He'd crossed a line,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.51,0:44:34.60,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>but I never sorted anything out.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.17,0:44:37.43,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>She sorted it out for me."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.56,0:44:39.35,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Babe?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.35,0:44:41.48,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,You home?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.26,0:44:44.31,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.74,0:44:47.92,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I got you some stuff from Bamboo House‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.01,0:44:51.05,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,You know those dumplings you like‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.49,0:44:55.67,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Babe?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.58,0:45:00.85,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"She was gone.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.80,0:45:05.07,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>And then the next day it happened."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.33,0:45:10.94,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"Professor Joseph Wieder was found dead.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.47,0:45:13.16,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Beaten to death.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.73,0:45:16.25,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Some junkie confessed to the crime."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.83,0:45:27.26,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"The Waterford College community digested the tragedy</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.39,0:45:30.44,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>and I went on to become a novelist of no repute,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.44,0:45:33.23,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>toiling in obscurity."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.14,0:45:40.71,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"And Laura Baines?</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.84,0:45:42.76,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I later found out that a week before the murder</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.89,0:45:44.37,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>she went to see Susan Avery,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.50,0:45:46.50,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Wieder's contact at the Department of Defense,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.63,0:45:48.50,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>claiming ownership over Wieder's work."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.63,0:45:50.33,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't work like that‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.46,0:45:51.94,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,The US Government commissioned the study‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.07,0:45:53.29,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,The grant is for Professor Wieder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.42,0:45:54.81,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,But I wrote it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.99,0:45:57.64,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, Ms. Baines‎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.77,0:46:00.73,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know what arrangement you made with Dr. Wieder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.86,0:46:02.65,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,but I recommend you take it up with the university‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.78,0:46:03.82,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,or directly with him‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.95,0:46:05.61,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! This is my work‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.74,0:46:07.56,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,and he just put his name on it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.70,0:46:09.57,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry - Is that all you can say?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.70,0:46:10.92,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,This is bullshit‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.05,0:46:13.48,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't just get away with this‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.62,0:46:17.27,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"After the murder she disappeared.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.36,0:46:21.40,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>It was like she'd fallen right off the face of the Earth."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.19,0:46:25.19,Eng_green,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>"Until the day I saw her again."</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.02,0:46:28.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,"Until.. I saw her again."‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.20,0:46:34.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Until you saw her again where?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.59,0:46:38.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah, you motherfucker‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.74,0:46:56.27,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You know what? She's probably dead‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.40,0:46:59.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Her social security number is still active‎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.66,0:47:02.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She's got no address no social media presence‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.92,0:47:04.40,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,no place of business, nothing‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.53,0:47:06.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Just one old pic from high school‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.45,0:47:08.28,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So what? She's a private person‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.41,0:47:10.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It's the same with Wayne Devereaux‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.28,0:47:11.76,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wieder's caretaker‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.89,0:47:14.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No phone number no job history‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.28,0:47:16.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I did a reverse address search, nothing‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.07,0:47:19.64,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It's like everyone from Wieder's life at that time‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.77,0:47:21.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,is now a fucking ghost‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.90,0:47:23.12,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You know what?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.77,0:47:26.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You're making me feel like I want to be a fucking ghost‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.08,0:47:30.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,The only one I've been able to track down is Finn's ex-wife‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.91,0:47:32.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go and talk to her‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.69,0:47:35.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And what the fuck's she gonna say to you?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.61,0:47:36.70,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.26,0:47:38.74,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She might know something‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.22,0:47:41.62,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You know? Finn might have been onto something‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.75,0:47:44.18,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a lot of somethings and maybes and ifs and buts‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.31,0:47:47.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, man if Isaac Samuel is innocent‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.58,0:47:49.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and we've put away the wrong guy‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.88,0:47:51.28,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,come on‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.41,0:47:53.37,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a chance for us to make that right‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.50,0:47:56.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- The guy confessed - I know he confessed, okay?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.59,0:47:59.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He admits he was in the house on that night. He says that‎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.59,0:48:02.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But he also says before he could do anything‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.90,0:48:05.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,someone else came in to the house‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.38,0:48:06.64,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Who?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.77,0:48:08.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Who came in, Roy?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.03,0:48:11.30,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.43,0:48:12.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't fucking know‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.86,0:48:15.04,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,then I don't fucking know either‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.61,0:48:20.26,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take a piss‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.88,0:48:30.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>And he drops in another one!</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.58,0:48:32.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>This kid's on fire!</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.47,0:48:52.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.34,0:48:55.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What the fuck, man?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.95,0:48:58.39,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.04,0:49:06.96,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Hallucinations are often a common byproduct</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.09,0:49:08.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>of the procedure.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.88,0:49:11.36,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But I've only ever seen pictures of her‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.49,0:49:14.71,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, well it indicates recall‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.84,0:49:16.80,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,even if it wasn't really her‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.93,0:49:19.58,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Same with the snippets of memory you've reported‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.32,0:49:24.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It means your neural pathways are starting to reactivate‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.37,0:49:27.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So I'm not just going completely crazy, then?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.72,0:49:29.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Far from it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.68,0:49:32.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You're actually what we'd call a good result‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.90,0:49:34.29,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Treatment's working‎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.27,0:49:56.10,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,[man] Put that down‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.90,0:50:20.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Ms. Finn?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.47,0:50:21.56,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to disturb you. I..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.69,0:50:22.95,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You the cop?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.08,0:50:26.74,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Roy Freeman, yeah. I called‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.87,0:50:28.39,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm actually you know, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.52,0:50:30.39,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,...retired‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.52,0:50:32.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And so I'm not with the police anymore‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.92,0:50:35.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Good. Never liked cops‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.28,0:50:45.80,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Doesn't make sense.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.93,0:50:47.89,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Richard was a lot of things--‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.02,0:50:50.11,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,paranoid, deluded‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.80,0:50:52.68,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,real misanthrope‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.63,0:50:55.29,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But he wasn't a druggie‎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.29,0:51:00.86,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So you think his death was an accident, maybe?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.99,0:51:03.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I bet that cunt Elizabeth Westlake‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.38,0:51:04.82,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,had something to do with it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.74,0:51:12.00,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I-I don't know who that is‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.13,0:51:14.74,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Neither did I until recently‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.13,0:51:17.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Crazy-ass bitch‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.48,0:51:21.27,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,They had some big argument‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.40,0:51:23.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,a few weeks before Richard moved out‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.84,0:51:28.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Elizabeth... Westlake?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.10,0:51:31.28,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.[Roy] Yeah. Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.93,0:51:34.72,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Richard started drinking again‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.72,0:51:38.16,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And one night he comes home screaming on the phone‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.29,0:51:40.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,all pissed‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.20,0:51:41.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh. No, no, no‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.68,0:51:43.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, no‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.68,0:51:45.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, no you listen to me, okay?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.12,0:51:47.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't you fucking lie to me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.56,0:51:49.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>He must have thought I was asleep.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.30,0:51:52.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, I-I know what you did Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.34,0:51:54.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And you're not gonna get away with it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.96,0:51:58.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You ever ask him what the argument was about?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.40,0:52:04.27,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I tried not to talk to Richard when he was like that‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.27,0:52:06.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Right‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.58,0:52:13.06,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>So I waited until he was asleep.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.67,0:52:19.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Next day, I called the number,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.72,0:52:21.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and got her voicemail‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.59,0:52:23.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What else do you know about her?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.11,0:52:26.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Know what she does? Do you know how they connect?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.60,0:52:28.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- No - Nothing?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.16,0:52:30.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You just called her a crazy-ass bitch‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.86,0:52:32.91,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, all I know is I never heard him talk‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.04,0:52:34.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,to anybody like that before‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.04,0:52:37.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Not even me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.52,0:52:39.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You ask me..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.13,0:52:42.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,she killed him‎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.59,0:53:46.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Ms. Westlake‎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.15,0:53:49.63,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. Mr. Freeman‎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.90,0:53:55.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Have we met?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.16,0:53:58.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I have a condition‎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.99,0:54:00.08,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I forget a lot of stuff‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.73,0:54:02.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.60,0:54:04.30,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We met in passing a long time ago‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.43,0:54:07.04,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And I'd read about your accident in the newspaper‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.18,0:54:11.22,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Would you mind if I asked you where?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.18,0:54:13.96,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Where did we meet? - I wish I could talk‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.09,0:54:15.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But I need to get to the office‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.44,0:54:16.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,That's okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.79,0:54:18.19,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I actually just wanted to talk to you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.32,0:54:19.49,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,about Richard Finn‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.02,0:54:26.80,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, there's someone I'd like to forget‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.37,0:54:28.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Why is that?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.63,0:54:31.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess you've never been stalked‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.85,0:54:32.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,made to feel like you always‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.07,0:54:34.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,need to be looking over your shoulder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.59,0:54:37.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah, well you know, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.55,0:54:40.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,he had it in his mind‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.51,0:54:44.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,that you had something to do with Joseph Wieder's murder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.69,0:54:49.04,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So you've spoken to him?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.57,0:54:52.00,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I haven't. Uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.92,0:54:54.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I tried to but he passed away‎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.92,0:54:59.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- I see - Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.01,0:55:01.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He left something behind, though‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.01,0:55:03.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,A memoir‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.88,0:55:05.84,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if you'd like to have a look at it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.97,0:55:07.63,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You could just tell me what you think‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.76,0:55:10.28,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I've worked very hard to forget that time in my life‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.41,0:55:12.89,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Professor Wieder's death and I'd rather not relive it‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.02,0:55:15.02,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Totally understand. Yeah‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.76,0:55:17.33,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, though, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.03,0:55:20.29,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,there is a man who is on death row‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.42,0:55:21.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,for Joseph Wieder's murder‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.90,0:55:23.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and his date's coming up pretty soon‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.12,0:55:30.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So maybe you could just you know, take a look‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.83,0:55:35.87,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,If I have a free moment‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.61,0:55:38.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Great. Thank you Thank you very much‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.92,0:55:40.57,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Alright - Alright‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.70,0:55:41.83,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You have a great day‎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.70,0:55:44.71,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You take care of yourself now, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.15,0:57:18.84,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,This is it, man‎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.44,0:58:39.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Devereaux?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.59,0:58:49.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Devereaux?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.99,0:59:04.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It's been a while‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.65,0:59:06.08,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Took me a second there to place you‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.21,0:59:07.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but my story's the same as it was then‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.60,0:59:09.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I just never got to tell it to you 'cause..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.78,0:59:12.22,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,you already had your man‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.35,0:59:14.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, if it's okay with you I'd like to hear it now‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.92,0:59:17.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah? Why is that?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.27,0:59:19.27,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm just going back through things‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.79,0:59:21.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Making sure all the right boxes got checked‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.92,0:59:23.23,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,you know?‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.06,0:59:26.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.06,0:59:28.41,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well..‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.19,0:59:30.71,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Professor Wieder found me‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.85,0:59:32.76,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>when I was a shell of who I was.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.89,0:59:35.11,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>He helped me get back on my feet.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.24,0:59:37.37,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>He got me a job working maintenance.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.50,0:59:40.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I mean, I remember it crystal clear, man.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.68,0:59:42.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>He was like a celebrity.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.68,0:59:43.81,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Everyone loved him.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.73,0:59:50.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>He did all sorts of work.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.17,0:59:52.56,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I don't know what exactly,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.69,0:59:54.09,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>but there was always people visiting.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.22,0:59:56.35,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you so much‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.48,0:59:58.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Important people.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.26,0:59:59.83,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>People from the government,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.96,1:00:01.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Department of Defense‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.92,1:00:03.18,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He was running a trial for them‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.31,1:00:04.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,out of his department at the college‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.66,1:00:06.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Trauma patients‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.27,1:00:08.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Testing a medication he developed‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.14,1:00:10.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess I was a perfect candidate‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.28,1:00:14.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I was first on the ground in Iraq.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.28,1:00:16.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Saw my share of it before taking a bullet.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.63,1:00:19.11,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't know the real damage till I got home‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.24,1:00:20.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Just couldn't get right‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.11,1:00:22.24,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wieder found me at the VA‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.38,1:00:24.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,said I fit his research profile‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.81,1:00:27.08,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What kind of research?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.21,1:00:31.12,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wayne, what if I told you‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.25,1:00:33.82,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,that through medicine and suggestion‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.95,1:00:37.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,you could replace the memory of your trauma of Iraq‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.65,1:00:40.09,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,with better memories‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.22,1:00:45.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,or perhaps erase the memory of your trauma altogether?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.92,1:00:50.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Man, I'd say sign me up‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.75,1:00:54.58,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,By activating opposite sides of the brain‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.32,1:00:58.02,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,we can release the emotional experiences‎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.15,1:01:00.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,trapped in our nervous system‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.59,1:01:04.24,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But before we make that bad memory go away‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.07,1:01:08.12,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,we have to fully confront it‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.64,1:01:10.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Breathe‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.99,1:01:17.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He said it was effective for dealing with PTSD‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.82,1:01:20.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but that was only part of the treatment‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.04,1:01:23.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Take one in the morning‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.26,1:01:27.09,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And one before bed‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.88,1:01:30.27,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>The rest was that medication he developed.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.40,1:01:33.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>He said it could wipe the slate clean.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.14,1:01:36.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>But you just told me about Iraq.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.01,1:01:38.80,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Does that mean the treatment didn't work?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.67,1:01:41.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, it did for a time‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.58,1:01:44.24,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Details faded No more panic attacks‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.37,1:01:45.72,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But those pills, man I mean..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.33,1:01:50.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>...they had some fucking mean side effects.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.25,1:01:53.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I didn't recognize myself anymore.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.90,1:01:55.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I'd black out.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.34,1:01:57.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No idea where I was how I got there‎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.91,1:02:00.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So you stopped taking the medication?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.60,1:02:01.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Mm-hm‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.00,1:02:04.87,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, against the professor's wishes‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.26,1:02:07.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Where's your car?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.92,1:02:10.00,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I came here by taxi‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.09,1:02:12.62,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You want a ride?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.75,1:02:14.23,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,ASPCA in the city buys my offcuts for dogs‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.36,1:02:18.27,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- You sure? - Yeah, man. Seat's free‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.93,1:02:28.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about Laura Baines?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.28,1:02:32.11,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, man. I don't think anybody ever really knew Laura Baines‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.24,1:02:33.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Her and Wieder were a thing, yeah?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.68,1:02:35.33,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know nothin' about that‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.46,1:02:37.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,From what he said, she's just a lab assistant, nothing more‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.68,1:02:39.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, maybe she'd like to be‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.34,1:02:40.90,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But if they were I never saw it‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.73,1:02:43.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Not that I didn't see others.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.69,1:02:46.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I'd come over the house every now and then,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.74,1:02:48.04,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>to fix this and that.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.88,1:02:59.58,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>There were a lot of women.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.32,1:03:02.06,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He kept a record of them too‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.14,1:03:04.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What kind of record?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.54,1:03:09.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>He had one of those old-school camcorders.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.55,1:03:15.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I guess he liked to revisit his past exploits.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.03,1:03:19.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Did Laura Baines ever call him out on it?</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.60,1:03:22.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No, man. Only time I heard them exchange words‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.16,1:03:24.82,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,was over some research paper they were writing‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.95,1:03:27.91,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But the night he was killed her and Finn‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.04,1:03:29.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>they came over to the house</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.65,1:03:31.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>and there was some kind of argument.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.78,1:03:34.04,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We need to have a rational conversation‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.18,1:03:35.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,without all this accusation‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.79,1:03:37.87,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You're fucking lying![Laura] He's not lying‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.01,1:03:40.05,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Oh! You wanna defend him now? - I don't need defending‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.18,1:03:41.40,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What were they fighting about?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.53,1:03:43.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuck if I know Finn got real pissed off‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.10,1:03:45.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Know what? Fuck the both of you‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.67,1:03:47.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- You deserve each other - Are you fucking kidding me?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.67,1:03:49.23,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>He left and I went to go out front,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.36,1:03:50.93,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>talk to him maybe see what's what.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.06,1:03:54.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But he was just... gone‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.28,1:03:56.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Or he never left‎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.85,1:04:02.29,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,In Finn's statement he says he was home alone‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.42,1:04:04.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,at the time of the murder‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.34,1:04:06.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, I can only tell you what I saw‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.86,1:04:09.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What about Laura? You see her leave?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.38,1:04:10.91,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, later in a taxi‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.82,1:04:13.95,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So where'd you go?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.08,1:04:16.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,My usual. Old Warren‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.78,1:04:20.92,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>The bartender there, Diane,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.48,1:04:23.70,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>even she was one of the professor's girls.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.05,1:04:27.18,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He was a good man‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.75,1:04:29.71,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He lost his way that's all‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.10,1:04:33.28,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It can happen to any one of us‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.41,1:04:35.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But it's like the Bible says‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.54,1:04:38.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,"Do not judge lest you too be judged."‎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.37,1:04:43.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks for the lift‎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.97,1:05:13.58,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's me‎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.97,1:05:16.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He's home‎
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.06,1:06:02.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Diane Lynch‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.39,1:07:11.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,A very, very interesting read‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.35,1:07:15.92,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna invite me in?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.02,1:07:28.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Can I get you a water?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.45,1:07:29.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe some whiskey‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.76,1:07:33.11,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I, uh... I don't have any in the house‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.24,1:07:34.72,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Doctors. [chuckles]‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.85,1:07:36.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't even remember the last time I had a drink‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.07,1:07:39.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,One of the few benefits of your condition, I suppose‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.07,1:07:41.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't remember the bad times‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.21,1:07:44.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Can't remember the good times, either‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.38,1:07:45.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,That's too bad‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.60,1:07:51.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Must be hard--‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.61,1:07:54.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,no memory of friends, family past experience‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.61,1:07:58.57,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No context for who you are Your place in the world‎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.75,1:08:01.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't imagine what that's like‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.88,1:08:04.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,to feel so lost‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.23,1:08:07.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So alone‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.97,1:08:11.19,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So what did you think of Finn's book?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.76,1:08:16.24,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It was..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.72,1:08:18.76,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,a bunch of bullshit‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.60,1:08:28.64,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So, you two were uh... never lovers?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.12,1:08:31.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No. That was just his little fantasy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.13,1:08:35.22,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,People make things up all the time‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.35,1:08:37.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Lie to protect themselves‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.26,1:08:40.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Manufacture histories to appear more than they are‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.40,1:08:43.57,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,'cause the reality is too painful‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.36,1:08:48.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- I spoke with Wayne Devereaux - Hmm‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.66,1:08:50.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He seemed to confirm a lot of what's in there‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.80,1:08:54.10,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wow. Another reliable witness Makes sense, though‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.23,1:08:56.02,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Lots of vets who suffer from trauma‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.15,1:08:58.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,turn to escapist invention-- video games‎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.80,1:09:00.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,pornography‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.28,1:09:02.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So, did he invent the research study‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.55,1:09:03.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wieder was working on too?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.07,1:09:06.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No. Wayne was a participant in that‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.33,1:09:07.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But if I remember correctly‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.12,1:09:11.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,he didn't respond favorably to the protocol‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.25,1:09:14.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He resented what it did to him‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.34,1:09:17.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He was prone to bouts of anger, aggression‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.47,1:09:19.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You seem to know a whole lot about him‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.30,1:09:22.87,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I transcribed Wieder's patient notes. All of them‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.44,1:09:26.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Sometimes you learn things you'd prefer you didn't‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.01,1:09:28.49,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He said that Wieder was intending‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.62,1:09:30.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,on publishing his findings, so..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.44,1:09:32.40,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what you do You work for years‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.53,1:09:33.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and then you publish your findings‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.01,1:09:36.80,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But he died before it was complete‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.15,1:09:42.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you feel he was giving you the credit you deserved?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.98,1:09:46.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He died before we could work that out as well‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.20,1:09:54.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,A drug that can help people forget past trauma‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.99,1:09:57.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Seems to me someone could make‎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.34,1:09:59.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,a whole lot of money out of that‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.08,1:10:02.56,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Now you think someone killed him for money‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.91,1:10:05.91,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You may not have memory Mr. Freeman‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.05,1:10:08.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but you do have quite the imagination‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.31,1:10:14.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,People kill for a whole lot of different reasons‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.71,1:10:20.10,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I reached out to Susan Avery‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.23,1:10:21.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wieder's DOD contact‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.80,1:10:23.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I know who Susan Avery is‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.63,1:10:25.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She collaborated with Wieder for decades‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.72,1:10:27.11,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So then you also know‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.24,1:10:29.90,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,that she's taken over his department at Waterford‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.03,1:10:33.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hmm‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.77,1:10:37.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, this conversation would have been a lot better‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.12,1:10:39.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,with whiskey‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.17,1:10:46.26,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You used to love a good drink, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.66,1:10:54.05,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Now call the play.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.18,1:10:56.84,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll give you five seconds to unbuckle your guns‎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.88,1:11:00.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,One‎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.75,1:11:01.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Two‎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.62,1:11:03.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Three.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.10,1:11:05.58,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Enough fun Unbuckle them.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.71,1:11:07.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Harry Jackson, get the hardware.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.45,1:11:08.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Doc!</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.85,1:11:12.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Anybody else want to try their luck?</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.16,1:11:15.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Get moving!</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.64,1:11:17.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Come on, keep moving all of ya!</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.08,1:12:48.69,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, fuck‎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.95,1:12:54.87,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>911. What's your emergency?</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.00,1:12:57.39,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh, I wanna report a shooting‎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.65,1:13:00.70,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Freeman, I'm going to read you your rights‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.39,1:13:03.35,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You have the right to remain silent‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.48,1:13:05.05,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,If you refuse this right‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.18,1:13:08.10,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,anything you say can be used against you in a court of law‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.23,1:13:10.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You have the right to an attorney‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.27,1:13:11.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,If you cannot afford an attorney‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.80,1:13:13.49,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,one will be appointed to you by the court‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.98,1:13:26.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We all done?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.51,1:13:29.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Case closed‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.64,1:13:31.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Another one off the books‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.55,1:13:34.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go celebrate I'm buying‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.21,1:13:39.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let me catch you up‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.96,1:13:42.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll wait for you in the car‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.83,1:13:49.27,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,If you cannot afford an attorney‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.40,1:13:51.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,one will be appointed to you by the court‎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.79,1:13:54.10,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you understand the rights I just read to you, sir?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.11,1:14:07.63,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You know you're one lucky sonofabitch‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.90,1:14:12.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Those security cameras caught him trying to run you down‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.55,1:14:14.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,There's gonna be a lot of red tape‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.16,1:14:18.08,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but, uh, it'll prove it's self-defense‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.60,1:14:21.91,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming down‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.04,1:14:23.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, course‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.26,1:14:26.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You'd have done exactly the same thing for me‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.00,1:14:31.92,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,CSI found two vials of fentanyl‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.05,1:14:33.62,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,in Devereaux's truck--‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.75,1:14:35.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,the same shit that killed Finn‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.40,1:14:38.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,They're calling it a homicide‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.23,1:14:41.19,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.80,1:14:45.19,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Devereaux killed Finn?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.32,1:14:46.72,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,For what?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.54,1:14:50.68,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop him IDing him for Wieder's murder?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.81,1:14:53.38,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure. Makes sense‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.51,1:14:56.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No. No, it doesn't make fuckin' sense‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.60,1:14:59.12,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,In his own goddamn book‎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.25,1:15:02.86,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Finn is pointing 100% to Elizabeth Westlake‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.99,1:15:04.00,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,not to Devereaux‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.65,1:15:09.00,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Something's not right‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.00,1:15:11.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, something's not right‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.18,1:15:14.05,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Something's not right with you, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.57,1:15:19.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Isaac Samuel committed this act‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.58,1:15:23.06,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Isaac Samuel confessed to it‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.19,1:15:25.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,In one month‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.54,1:15:29.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,there will be justice and he will be dead‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.59,1:15:34.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And you can move on and forget about all this‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.78,1:15:49.26,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Was I a good cop?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.35,1:15:53.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Were you a good cop? What?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.74,1:15:55.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What the fuck are you talking about?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.22,1:15:58.92,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Was I good at my job?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.05,1:16:01.18,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Or was I a bad cop? Was I a shit cop?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.31,1:16:02.84,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Was I a lazy sonofabitch‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.97,1:16:05.40,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,who just marked his card and showed up?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.53,1:16:08.84,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Roy, you were one of the best‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.97,1:16:10.76,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You were a great cop‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.11,1:16:18.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,My name's not on any of the sign-offs‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.59,1:16:19.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.72,1:16:21.33,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,In the Wieder file‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.46,1:16:24.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,My name is not on any of the officials‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.69,1:16:27.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Not the incident report..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.78,1:16:30.04,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,not the witness sheet‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.17,1:16:33.35,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,forensic findings Samuel's confession‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.48,1:16:34.82,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,None of it‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.44,1:16:37.83,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It's just your name..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.35,1:16:40.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,on all of it‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.92,1:16:45.10,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say, Roy?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.84,1:16:49.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been going back through 30 years of case files‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.45,1:16:50.67,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Thirty years‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.28,1:16:54.37,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Every one, every document every single one..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.54,1:16:57.24,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,we co-signed‎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.37,1:16:59.37,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,My name right next to yours‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.29,1:17:01.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Except for this one‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.29,1:17:04.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Why is that?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.73,1:17:11.12,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I see what you're doing here Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.99,1:17:15.08,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You've interviewed everyone else‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.17,1:17:18.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Now you're gonna accuse me‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.13,1:17:21.26,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.39,1:17:23.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,you're some fuckin' piece of work‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.27,1:17:27.92,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You come to my house out of nowhere‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.05,1:17:29.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,asking for my help‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.92,1:17:32.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and now you accuse me?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.76,1:17:38.24,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuck you, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.54,1:17:41.06,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuck you‎
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.08,1:19:29.87,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I ain't no killer‎
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.32,1:19:52.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You're in rare form tonight‎
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.68,1:19:54.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Where is she?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.11,1:19:57.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She won't be coming in for a while, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.05,1:21:46.92,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Okay - Uh-huh‎
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.75,1:21:50.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm out‎
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.14,1:21:52.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, don't take my car, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.27,1:21:54.49,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey I will bring it back tomorrow‎
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.84,1:22:00.93,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What you did I will never forget‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.29,1:22:06.24,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomorrow‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.16,1:22:16.08,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We're not open yet‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.30,1:22:23.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Was there an old gray-haired guy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.56,1:22:24.70,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,used to run this place?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.83,1:22:27.05,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Eric? Eric O'Toole?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.18,1:22:29.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's retired. Is there anything I can help you with?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.01,1:22:31.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It's my pop's place now‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.66,1:22:34.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm looking for a woman who used to work here too‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.45,1:22:37.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Her name's Diane - Oh, you mean Diane Lynch?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.58,1:22:40.06,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. Any idea where I could find her?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.19,1:22:42.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, just over at Calvary Catholic‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.72,1:22:46.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She died about five years ago‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.98,1:22:49.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't say?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.03,1:22:51.81,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuck‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.94,1:22:53.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Was she a friend or something?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.86,1:22:58.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Eh, she gave a deposition in a case I was working on‎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.38,1:23:00.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- I was just following up - So, you a cop?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.60,1:23:01.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Used to be‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.13,1:23:04.30,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Well..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.52,1:23:06.87,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,On me‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.04,1:23:09.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,My grandfather was a cop‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.40,1:23:18.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I just recently remembered I actually, uh..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.45,1:23:20.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I like to do this‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.58,1:23:21.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't we all?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.36,1:23:24.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,To Diane‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.46,1:23:33.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey You mind if I use your bathroom?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.90,1:23:36.16,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Just around the corner other side of the jukebox‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.29,1:23:37.33,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.40,1:23:59.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello? <i>Mr. Freeman?</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.14,1:24:01.71,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>It's Susan Avery returning your call.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.84,1:24:03.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Blunt object to the head‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.10,1:24:07.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, Susan? <i>From Waterford College.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.58,1:24:09.63,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I have something for you.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.24,1:24:18.55,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You sure I can't get you a glass of water?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.68,1:24:20.16,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm fine‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.33,1:24:23.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You said you had something for me?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.69,1:24:29.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know where the original is‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.30,1:24:31.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Probably in storage at the DOD, if I had to guess‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.26,1:24:33.87,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but that's the only copy I had from my time there‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.00,1:24:35.44,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>The Mirror Effect.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.57,1:24:37.57,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wieder was quite proud of this work‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.70,1:24:39.00,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He thought it would help people‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.13,1:24:40.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,who were suffering with their trauma‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.75,1:24:42.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- It's award-worthy research - It was never published?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.44,1:24:44.23,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,At least not under his name‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.36,1:24:46.40,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't understand‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.67,1:24:50.49,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I gather you haven't read her book‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.10,1:24:53.89,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She updated Wieder's research with additional findings‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.02,1:24:55.11,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,she culled together over the years‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.24,1:24:56.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,she was getting her doctorate‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.67,1:24:58.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So, she stole his work?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.33,1:25:00.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It happens all the time in academic research‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.72,1:25:02.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides, who would protest?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.90,1:25:05.47,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- Wieder's dead - But you contracted it?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.60,1:25:07.95,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not as simple as that‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.08,1:25:09.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Before Wieder died‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.56,1:25:11.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Laura Baines came to me with that manuscript‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.38,1:25:13.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard she wasn't happy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.73,1:25:15.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>She claimed the work was hers.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.26,1:25:17.26,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wieder wasn't giving her the credit she deserved‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.39,1:25:20.57,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,This is bullshit! He can't just get away with this‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.31,1:25:22.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So, how did she publish it?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.79,1:25:24.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We'd been circulating it‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.14,1:25:25.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,in a number of the VA hospitals‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.79,1:25:28.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,but the department's priorities changed‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.14,1:25:30.49,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,A few years later after I started working here‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.62,1:25:32.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I found her book review‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.27,1:25:36.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So... why didn't you go after her?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.45,1:25:38.50,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,There was nothing to go after her for‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.63,1:25:40.41,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,The project was shuttered‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.37,1:25:46.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wieder used to live around here, right?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.33,1:25:49.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Over on Chestnut. Apparently the house is still empty‎
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.68,1:26:27.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Blunt object to the head‎
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.42,1:26:33.07,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Any sign of it?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.21,1:26:36.25,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No. Couple of bats in the garage, though‎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.24,1:27:05.89,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,One's missing, right?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.02,1:27:08.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Caretaker there said they were all signed by Hall of Famers‎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.72,1:27:11.24,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,so probably worth a lot of money‎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.55,1:27:14.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You wanna go talk to him?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.12,1:27:18.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- I will. Come on - Sir‎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.15,1:29:20.94,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What you got there, Roy?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.99,1:29:26.60,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Never did find the murder weapon‎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.73,1:29:29.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,from the Wieder case, did you?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.95,1:29:32.30,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You put this here?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.91,1:29:35.43,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Put it back in the hole, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.66,1:29:48.18,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Both of youse, get inside‎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.49,1:29:54.45,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Why couldn't you just listen to me?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.58,1:29:56.89,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You just couldn't let it go could you?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.54,1:29:59.63,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What did you do, Jim?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.76,1:30:01.02,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What did I do?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.98,1:30:04.11,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I cleaned this fucking mess up‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.24,1:30:07.64,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Ten years ago. Don't you remember any of this?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.77,1:30:10.38,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,- What Diane did? - Diane?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.12,1:30:12.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She told me what you knew‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.73,1:30:14.86,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Diane Lynch?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.99,1:30:16.86,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Get away from me‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.99,1:30:18.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,From your favorite bar‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.65,1:30:20.56,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She was one of Wieder's patients‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.69,1:30:22.04,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Enough, Laura‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.17,1:30:24.74,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I told you I would take care of this‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.79,1:30:30.09,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.66,1:30:34.19,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You know each other?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.58,1:30:38.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I see‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.10,1:30:40.63,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So, you're in this together?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.15,1:30:44.06,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuck me.[Roy] No, I get it‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.20,1:30:45.76,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I get it, Jimmy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.72,1:30:48.42,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Your wife got really sick‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.55,1:30:49.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You got deep in debt‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.90,1:30:51.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She comes along pays to you kill Wieder‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.99,1:30:53.73,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,so she can publish her book‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.86,1:30:56.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and you you railroad Isaac Samuel‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.34,1:30:57.90,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,cover it all up‎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.04,1:31:01.21,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no. I did not pay him to kill Wieder‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.13,1:31:04.82,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,We didn't meet until after your accident‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.78,1:31:08.52,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>My life was destroyed.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.57,1:31:12.61,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I was facing losing years of clinical research.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.75,1:31:14.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,The name "Laura Baines"‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.27,1:31:16.58,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,would always be associated with what happened‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.71,1:31:20.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Then your partner showed up asking all kinds of questions.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.88,1:31:22.58,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>I didn't know what he wanted but he wouldn't let up</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.71,1:31:24.19,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>and I was so scared.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.32,1:31:25.76,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, fuck you, Laura‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.50,1:31:30.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So, I... left‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.98,1:31:33.90,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I moved, changed my name started over‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.03,1:31:36.90,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,completed the research and published <i>my</i> book‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.03,1:31:39.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,hoping I would never see him again‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.47,1:31:40.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>But then, a few years ago,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.90,1:31:42.82,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Richard Finn started poking around.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.95,1:31:46.17,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She's an author Elizabeth Westlake‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.78,1:31:49.04,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,But she changed it It used to be Laura Baines‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.17,1:31:51.22,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>She must have taken Wieder's work after he died.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.35,1:31:53.79,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>You ask me she's the one who killed him.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.35,1:31:57.92,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Then somehow your partner found me</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.05,1:31:59.88,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>and he turned up with his hand out,</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.01,1:32:02.06,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and this time, it's for money‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.19,1:32:05.75,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,All this, all this is just fucking bullshit, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.89,1:32:08.71,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not lying He blackmailed me‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.84,1:32:11.72,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He said he'd go public with proof my book wasn't my work‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.85,1:32:13.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,unless I paid him‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.81,1:32:16.46,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,So, you killed Richard Finn too‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.59,1:32:18.59,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,in case he got the same idea?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.72,1:32:20.90,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't kill anyone‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.03,1:32:24.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She killed Finn the same way she killed Wieder‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.47,1:32:26.95,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Finn's writing a book about the murder‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.08,1:32:29.39,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and he thinks you killed Wieder‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.52,1:32:30.87,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,You need to talk to him‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.00,1:32:33.13,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>With other people's hands.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.26,1:32:34.35,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.48,1:32:36.22,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, Laura‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.35,1:32:38.48,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,you can fuck around all you want, but I'm not..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.61,1:32:41.36,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Devereaux was already a trained killer.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.49,1:32:43.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>With Finn out of the way she got him to come after you.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.10,1:32:45.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,He's home‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.10,1:32:49.15,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait until he leaves and then take care of it‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.97,1:32:53.76,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She's a manipulator, Roy‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.89,1:32:57.02,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She's manipulating you right now‎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.15,1:33:00.03,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She gets people to come in and do her dirty work‎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.16,1:33:01.81,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and then she just skates away‎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.94,1:33:04.86,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,She has to be held accountable‎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.69,1:33:18.65,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Hm, it's such a funny thing the mind‎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.78,1:33:21.31,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,the things it can live with‎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.44,1:33:24.09,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,and the things it just can't bear‎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.05,1:33:26.44,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,To get to die ignorant of both‎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.57,1:33:28.01,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,now that..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.14,1:33:31.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, that is a special kind of bliss‎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.48,1:34:07.96,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,What I did..‎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.75,1:34:12.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,I did for you‎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.57,1:34:55.53,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Breaking news in a decades-old murder</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.66,1:34:57.14,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>out at Waterford College</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.27,1:34:58.97,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>as fresh evidence in the brutal killing</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.10,1:35:01.32,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>of psychology professor Joseph Wieder</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.45,1:35:04.28,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>exonerates a man incarcerated on death row.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.20,1:35:09.85,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>29-year-old Isaac Samuel was convicted of revenge killing</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.98,1:35:12.11,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>and was scheduled to die by lethal injection</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.25,1:35:14.16,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>in just one month's time.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.08,1:35:20.78,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>But information uncovered in the wake of a double homicide</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.91,1:35:23.34,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>this past Tuesday at Wieder's abandoned home</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.47,1:35:25.56,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>tells a different kind of story.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.69,1:35:28.09,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Name three objects in this room.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.22,1:35:32.83,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Chair, lamp... clock‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.96,1:35:35.66,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,And three objects not in this room‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.18,1:35:40.58,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Wine glass, newspaper, gun‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.75,1:35:44.41,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Today's date?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.54,1:35:46.54,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,October 21st‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.11,1:35:49.98,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Your place of birth?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.11,1:35:51.89,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Larksville, Pennsylvania‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.42,1:35:54.77,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Your mother's name?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.90,1:35:56.20,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Florence‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.38,1:35:58.51,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Your father's name?‎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.64,1:35:59.99,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,George‎
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.95,1:36:03.38,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Your middle school?‎
