Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.26,1:38:20.30,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,<i>Professor Wieder is a doctor. He took an oath.</i>‎
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.43,1:38:23.09,Eng_gray,NTP,0,0,0,,Keep them from harm and injustice‎
